qas.question: At what airport was Schwarzenegger's jet forced to make an emergency landing in 2009?

context: Schwarzenegger's private jet made an emergency landing at <a0_0>Van Nuys Airport<a0_0/> on June 19, 2009, after the pilot reported smoke coming from the cockpit, according to a statement released by the governor's press secretary. No one was harmed in the incident.
